{"tid":1196243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"辣退左 分享下個人經驗","createTime":"2019-06-09T18:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T18:49:44.000Z","uid":147721,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cd6a0110e9232b89868d68c085dd307a61de1914","tid":1196243,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:33:04.000Z","msg":"麻辣火鍋雖然好好食 但係大家都知道 有時太滾既話 滾起晒啲水花會傷到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n眼罩就肯定可以保護到眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係大家唔好以為長衫長褲就唔會傷到手腳<br />\n因為啲辣汁雖然一開始無野 但係醃下醃下會好痛 好似燒傷咁痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個時候狂沖水都無咩用 除非你有五十支水係身邊啦<br />\n所以我建議大家 選擇一啲唔透既衣物 例如膠風褸 膠雨褸咁<br />\n如果不幸淺到辣汁 唔好亂咁掂身體其他部位 唔好亂用水沖 而係首先用乾紙巾/毛巾移走大部分辣汁先 然後先沖水 沖水個時個水流一定唔可以流經敏感既部位 例如嘴脣 耳 等等<br />\n用過既毛巾唔好on99用去其他人到"},{"pid":"bef812e7a940465ab256e49f01c40ceba9877733","tid":1196243,"uid":174283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:34:40.000Z","msg":"見你件咁嘅衫都知出事啦"},{"pid":"11787dc249073b350f663daeac89497f57591063","tid":1196243,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af469460c9ad5d68ba6c70c07b9380f0d5354ec","tid":1196243,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bef812e7a940465ab256e49f01c40ceba9877733","tid":1196243,"uid":174283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:34:40.000Z","msg":"見你件咁嘅衫都知出事啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17d889d86d109658235ae1dcc38724b2b2781a6","tid":1196243,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi